{"tid":2383481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福奇Fauci資助的功能增強研究導致新冠病毒大流行","createTime":"2021-01-28T02:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T08:12:06.000Z","uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e7568e6f1b79fcb472e433257bf23bfacc0aa04a","tid":2383481,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"福克斯新聞主持人史蒂夫&bull;希爾頓在周日晚間的節目中，以冠狀病毒起源的驚人進展開場。<br />\n<br />\n希爾頓討論了功能性增強研究，該研究有助於界定人類與病原體相互作用的基本性質。研究功能性增強科學的最大的實驗室之一，是位於中共國的武漢病毒研究所。<br />\n<br />\n功能性增強研究備受爭議。2014年，奧巴馬政府削減了對這項高風險生物研究的資助。聯邦研究實驗室發生生物安全事件後，政府做出了這一決定。<br />\n<br />\nGateway Pundit曾報導，奧巴馬政府在美國項目被關閉後，向武漢病毒學研究所提供了370萬美元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2021/01/steve-hilton-report-dr-anthony-fauci-directly-responsible-funding-gain-function-studies-resulted-coronavirus-pandemic-video/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatewaypundit.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fsteve-hilton-report-dr-anthony-fauci-directly-responsible-funding-gain-function-studies-resulted-coronavirus-pandemic-video%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=c2c307ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2021/01/steve-hilton-report-dr-anthony-fauci-directly-responsible-funding-gain-function-studies-resulted-coronavirus-pandemic-video/</a>"},{"pid":"281bd814121b6bd4814e64788d27ba26902e5ad6","tid":2383481,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHTLwDF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHTLwDF.png&h=40c9c670&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed6b253941607ff473d7312c1feb45da9e332eb6","tid":2383481,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D73jA9Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD73jA9Q.png&h=b196ec5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cafdf